<h1 style="font-size:20px; line-height:22px; height:22px; margin-bottom:10px;">木瓜</h1>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a> </p>
<div class="contson" id="contson478043ea449a">
投我以木瓜，报之以琼琚。匪报也，永以为好也！<br />投我以木桃，报之以琼瑶。匪报也，永以为好也！<br />投我以木李，报之以琼玖。匪报也，永以为好也！
</div>
</div>
