<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_a7e1ebce8d01.aspx"><b>明月何皎皎</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e4%b8%a4%e6%b1%89">两汉</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contsona7e1ebce8d01">
<p>明月何皎皎，照我罗床帏。<br />忧愁不能寐，揽衣起徘徊。<br />客行虽云乐，不如早旋归。<br />出户独彷徨，愁思当告谁！<br />引领还入房，泪下沾裳衣。</p>
