<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_18d68bd0d5a9.aspx"><b>梅花落</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%8d%97%e5%8c%97%e6%9c%9d">南北朝</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e9%b2%8d%e7%85%a7">鲍照</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contson18d68bd0d5a9">
中庭多杂树，偏为梅咨嗟。问君何独然？念其霜中能作花，露中能作实。摇荡春风媚春日，念尔零落逐寒风，徒有霜华无霜质。(寒风 一作：风飚)
</div>
